text.tspan: Based on the estimates and index by Polity 5 (2020), weighted by countries' populations. It captures the extent to
which open, multi-party, and competitive elections choose a chief executive who faces comprehensive institutional
constraints, and political participation is competitive. It here ranges from 0 to 20 (fully democratic).
